title: Nickelback_Live_Sturgis_2006.iso
description:
The Canadian Rockers performs at the Sturgis Biker Rally (Rock The Rally) in 2006. 

Full DVD

1.  Animals 
2.  Woke Up This morning 
3.  Photograph 
4.  Because of You 
5.  Far Away 
6.  Never Again 
7.  Savin' Me 
8.  Someday 
9.  Side of a Bullet 
10. How You Remind Me 
11. Too Bad 
12. Figured You Out 

Extras include "Behind the Scenes With Nickelback," "Sturgis 101 Vignette" and the "Rockstar" video.
